title: Halsocafet
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Organic, Raw, Salad bar, Juice bar, Take-out, Bakery, Catering, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. All salads, wraps, acai bowls and raw food bakery are 100% vegan and gluten free, as are the smoothies. Coffee is served with oat milk as a standard, but has a cow milk choice along with almond and soy. Everything on the menu is vegan or vegetarian and has both a soy protein and tofu to choose as extra protein. As of Dec 2015, salmon and chicken are also available as a protein choice. Chill atmosphere. Free Wi-Fi.
